          <span class="compare-eyebrow">Comparison · Last verified {lastVerified}</span>
          <h1>freee vs Money Forward Cloud for Japan SMEs</h1>
          <p class="compare-lead">
            These are Japan's two dominant cloud accounting platforms - and they're
            more different than they look. Here's the honest breakdown: pricing,
            compliance coverage, who each is actually built for, and what to ask
            before you pick one.
          </p>
          <div class="compare-meta">
            <span>By <a href="/about/" rel="author">Matt Ketchum</a></span>
            <span>·</span>
            <span>Tokyo</span>
